GET http://127.0.0.1:5000/

## Global Variables
@baseurl=http://127.0.0.1:5000

## Generate Description
# @name PostGenerateDescription
POST {{baseurl}}/descriptions/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "Smart Bottle 500ml",
  "features": [
    "Bebas BPA",
    "Menjaga suhu minuman 12 jam",
    "Tutup anti bocor"
  ],
  "platform": "Tokopedia",
  "tone": "persuasif"
}
###

## Response PostGenerateDescription
{
  "id": 1,
  "content": "Bawa gaya hidup sehatmu ke level berikutnya dengan Smart Bottle 500ml...",
  "created_at": "2026-04-22T14:00:00.000000",
  "request": {
    "id": 1,
    "product_name": "Smart Bottle 500ml",
    "features": [
      "Bebas BPA",
      "Menjaga suhu minuman 12 jam",
      "Tutup anti bocor"
    ],
    "platform": "Tokopedia",
    "tone": "persuasif",
    "created_at": "2026-04-22T14:00:00.000000"
  }
}
