## Open UI
GET {{baseurl}}/ui
Content-Type: application/json
###

## Get Descriptions
# @name GetDescriptions
GET {{baseurl}}/descriptions
Content-Type: application/json
###

POST https://openrouter.ai/api/v1/chat/completions
Authorization: Bearer sk-or-v1-xxxx
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": "openai/gpt-3.5-turbo",
  "messages": [
    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Halo"
    }
  ]
}

